      "content": "but there's nothing to find. that's the thing. there aren't any layers to peel back, there's just an empty room. it's like I've already died and I'm just a ghost haunting my own life. if there's no 'me' left to save, then isn't continuing the charade just... a waste of time? it's just constant, tiring noise for no reason.",
